---
title: Quick Coconut Katsu Pork & Udon Noodles with Veggies & Crispy Shallots
description: You’ll be off to visit your happy place when you get a taste of this dish. Pork mince is tossed in katsu paste and mellowed out with
coconut milk to create a perfectly balanced dish, with udon noodles to help slurp up all that sauce!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
